00:35:47,390 --> 00:35:50,830
It's tough being a big brother.

822
00:35:54,060 --> 00:35:57,370
Across the bridge it smells of soft rush reeds

823
00:35:57,370 --> 00:35:59,000
It's a tatami shop.

824
00:36:00,170 --> 00:36:02,640
Gyoden is down this road.

825
00:36:04,310 --> 00:36:05,910
The shop sign is within sight.

826
00:36:06,340 --> 00:36:08,280
He's already there.

827
00:36:08,610 --> 00:36:11,010
No way I can lose.

828
00:36:11,010 --> 00:36:14,880
He's getting fish of the season, squid and white-fleshed fish.

829
00:36:14,880 --> 00:36:19,560
For Chinatsu's first weaning meal, they will feed her white-fleshed fish.

830
00:36:19,560 --> 00:36:21,560
He has arrived at Gyoden.

831
00:36:21,560 --> 00:36:22,830
Good day.

832
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:27,730
Squid and delicious fish please.

833
00:36:26,130 --> 00:36:27,730
Looking for delicious fish?

834
00:36:28,100 --> 00:36:30,630
It's true that fish of the season are delicious.

835
00:36:30,630 --> 00:36:32,740
What's good today?

836
00:36:32,740 --> 00:36:37,040
Did your mother say grilled or boiled?

837
00:36:39,040 --> 00:36:41,310
Grilled.

838
00:36:39,610 --> 00:36:41,310
She said grilled?

839
00:36:41,310 --> 00:36:43,780
The recommendation changes based on preparation.

840
00:36:43,780 --> 00:36:47,720
A fishmonger that even sells to high-end restaurants.

841
00:36:47,720 --> 00:36:50,490
What grilling fish do you recommend today?

842
00:36:50,850 --> 00:36:53,590
Do you want this one? A pink colored fish.

843
00:36:53,590 --> 00:36:54,520
Cherry anthias.

844
00:36:54,520 --> 00:36:56,860
This one is so cute.

845
00:36:56,960 --> 00:37:00,530
What is it called?

846
00:36:59,130 --> 00:37:00,530
It's a sea bream.

847
00:37:00,900 --> 00:37:03,270
Then you want this one?

848
00:37:02,030 --> 00:37:03,270
Yeah.

849
00:37:03,270 --> 00:37:05,540
And squid, please.

850
00:37:06,500 --> 00:37:09,940
It's a young squid. Meaty and with a sweetness.

851
00:37:10,340 --> 00:37:11,710
Anything else?

852
00:37:11,710 --> 00:37:14,040
And perhaps some tuna.

853
00:37:12,780 --> 00:37:14,040
Bluefin tuna?

854
00:37:14,040 --> 00:37:17,010
His beloved bluefin tuna is rarely available here.

855
00:37:17,010 --> 00:37:19,010
The store boasts mostly local seafood.

856
00:37:19,010 --> 00:37:22,920
He doesn't know about largehead hairtails.

857
00:37:21,750 --> 00:37:23,920
It's really beautiful.

858
00:37:23,190 --> 00:37:24,620
What about this shrimp?

859
00:37:24,620 --> 00:37:25,960
Still can't eat those.

860
00:37:25,960 --> 00:37:27,960
Since Chinatsu is still a baby.

861
00:37:28,120 --> 00:37:29,390
And what about this crab?

862
00:37:29,390 --> 00:37:30,430
Also can't eat crabs.

863
00:37:30,430 --> 00:37:34,500
He was told that they can't feed her crustaceans yet.

864
00:37:33,860 --> 00:37:35,930
He understands all that.

865
00:37:34,600 --> 00:37:36,670
Is it fine with these two?

866
00:37:36,670 --> 00:37:39,870
And white-fleshed fish too.

867
00:37:37,970 --> 00:37:39,870
Yes, for Chinatsu.

868
00:37:40,700 --> 00:37:47,240
Since the sea bream is already a white-fleshed fish he ponders his next choice.

869
00:37:47,810 --> 00:37:52,950
I'm looking for an even whiter fish.

870
00:37:50,350 --> 00:37:52,950
An even whiter fish?

871
00:37:52,420 --> 00:37:54,050
Makes sense to him.

872
00:37:52,950 --> 00:37:55,320
Even with her fish expertise the old lady is struggling.

873
00:37:55,420 --> 00:37:58,990
A white one with no colors.

874
00:37:58,990 --> 00:38:01,920
He's looking for one that is white.

875
00:38:01,920 --> 00:38:04,430
A fish without a color? This one.

876
00:38:04,430 --> 00:38:05,460
Red tonguesole.

877
00:38:05,460 --> 00:38:07,530
Like this?

878
00:38:07,530 --> 00:38:09,800
But there's color on its backside.

879
00:38:09,800 --> 00:38:12,570
This is no good.

880
00:38:11,130 --> 00:38:12,570
He's harsh.

881
00:38:12,570 --> 00:38:13,940
Nitpicky.

882
00:38:14,370 --> 00:38:16,040
Like this?

883
00:38:16,040 --> 00:38:18,310
But there's color on its backside.

884
00:38:18,310 --> 00:38:21,640
This is no good.

885
00:38:19,210 --> 00:38:21,640
It's still a white-fleshed fish, though.

886
00:38:21,640 --> 00:38:23,510
He's nitpicking.

887
00:38:22,680 --> 00:38:24,050
But it becomes white.

888
00:38:24,050 --> 00:38:28,650
You peel the skin off and it's white beneath.

889
00:38:28,650 --> 00:38:30,220
I see.

890
00:38:29,350 --> 00:38:31,690
Do you want me to make it white for you?

891
00:38:31,690 --> 00:38:34,220
Can she do that?

892
00:38:34,220 --> 00:38:35,930
Please wait.

893
00:38:35,990 --> 00:38:38,390
But Rintarou really wants to watch.

894
00:38:38,390 --> 00:38:40,390
He's curious how she can make it white.

895
00:38:40,390 --> 00:38:44,170
Since I'm in giraffe class I want to watch.

896
00:38:44,170 --> 00:38:46,170
A morbid curiousity.

897
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:49,410
It will become white.

898
00:38:49,410 --> 00:38:51,140
It's his first time seeing it.

899
00:38:51,170 --> 00:38:52,810
Here I go.

900
00:38:52,810 --> 00:38:54,340
Removing the darkened skin.

901
00:38:54,340 --> 00:38:55,280
Heave ho.

902
00:38:55,280 --> 00:38:57,550
And it slips off.

903
00:38:57,550 --> 00:39:02,490
See, it become white. Isn't it good? It's white on both sides now.

904
00:38:57,780 --> 00:39:00,080
How pretty.

905
00:39:02,490 --> 00:39:04,350
But please cut off the blood.

906
00:39:04,990 --> 00:39:06,260
Cut off the blood?

907
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:07,620
He's making demands.

908
00:39:07,620 --> 00:39:10,090
Will you do the next one Rintarou?

909
00:39:10,090 --> 00:39:11,690
The cute fish.

910
00:39:11,690 --> 00:39:13,500
That's right.

911
00:39:13,500 --> 00:39:15,800
She's filleting the grilling fish.

912
00:39:16,530 --> 00:39:19,840
Poor fish looks in pain.

913
00:39:17,900 --> 00:39:19,840
In pain?

914
00:39:19,840 --> 00:39:20,800
Are you scared?

915
00:39:20,800 --> 00:39:22,670
Not scared.

916
00:39:21,670 --> 00:39:22,670
I see.

917
00:39:22,840 --> 00:39:26,480
I will watch since Rintarou is in giraffe class.

918
00:39:26,480 --> 00:39:31,150
His pride from being in giraffe class has strengthened Rintarou who usually loves being babied.

919
00:39:31,250 --> 00:39:33,420
He's staring at it now.

920
00:39:34,820 --> 00:39:36,090
Should I split it?

921
00:39:36,790 --> 00:39:39,020
He wasn't ready for that.

922
00:39:38,150 --> 00:39:39,020
Shock!

923
00:39:39,020 --> 00:39:40,690
But giving it his all.

924
00:39:41,160 --> 00:39:44,330
Rintarou farted.

925
00:39:44,330 --> 00:39:45,930
You just made a toot?

926
00:39:45,530 --> 00:39:47,200
The best.

927
00:39:46,730 --> 00:39:47,530
It smells.

928
00:39:47,530 --> 00:39:49,870
It smells?

929
00:39:49,870 --> 00:39:51,730
I'm wet for some reason.

930
00:39:51,730 --> 00:39:54,440
Old lady...

931
00:39:52,640 --> 00:39:54,440
Having overcome his embarrassment

932
00:39:54,740 --> 00:39:56,570
he has succeeded with the errand.

933
00:39:56,570 --> 00:39:58,240
It's ready.

934
00:39:58,240 --> 00:40:00,710
Let's see how much it amounts to.

935
00:40:00,840 --> 00:40:02,850
Time to pay.

936
00:40:02,850 --> 00:40:03,780
I...

937
00:40:03,780 --> 00:40:05,980
have this dried fish.

938
00:40:04,380 --> 00:40:05,980
The master has been observing.

939
00:40:05,980 --> 00:40:09,690
Will you taste it?

940
00:40:06,920 --> 00:40:09,690
And wants to give him delicious curry as a reward.

941
00:40:09,690 --> 00:40:10,920
Curry. Do you dislike curry?

942
00:40:11,090 --> 00:40:12,720
I dislike curry.

943
00:40:12,720 --> 00:40:15,530
I'm sorry for this in your busy schedule, master.

944
00:40:14,660 --> 00:40:17,360
It was a nice offer, though.

945
00:40:16,490 --> 00:40:18,090
It's fine with only 2000 yen.

946
00:40:19,660 --> 00:40:22,270
2000 yen.

947
00:40:20,430 --> 00:40:22,270
He bought all this for 2000 yen?

948
00:40:22,270 --> 00:40:24,270
It has been greatly discounted by the master.

949
00:40:24,270 --> 00:40:25,970
Thank you.

950
00:40:27,100 --> 00:40:31,410
Take care. Please come again.

951
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:33,880
Until next time.

952
00:40:35,280 --> 00:40:37,380
Thank you.

953
00:40:36,080 --> 00:40:37,380
Thank you.

954
00:40:37,380 --> 00:40:39,650
What a splendid shopping trip.

955
00:40:40,180 --> 00:40:43,650
The town of sun rays.

956
00:40:45,190 --> 00:40:49,960
I wonder if it will be sunny tomorrow.

957
00:40:49,960 --> 00:40:56,300
The paprika flowers are in bloom.

958
00:41:05,170 --> 00:41:06,940
His mood has changed.

959
00:41:06,940 --> 00:41:10,280
He crosses the bridge in a sunny mood.

960
00:41:10,510 --> 00:41:12,920
The anxious one is his mother.

961
00:41:12,920 --> 00:41:14,780
She keeps looking at the watch.

962
00:41:32,470 --> 00:41:34,470
Rintarou.

963
00:41:33,270 --> 00:41:34,470
It's his mothers voice.

964
00:41:34,470 --> 00:41:35,440
Where?

965
00:41:35,440 --> 00:41:37,570
Here. Above you.

966
00:41:38,110 --> 00:41:39,110
Did you go?

967
00:41:39,110 --> 00:41:40,340
I went.

968
00:41:40,340 --> 00:41:42,550
It's just a bit further.

969
00:41:47,620 --> 00:41:49,920
She looks delighted.

970
00:41:52,390 --> 00:41:58,130
The paprika flowers are in bloom.

971
00:41:58,560 --> 00:42:00,560
Please have a look at this face.

972
00:42:04,300 --> 00:42:07,140
Please look at his posture.

973
00:42:07,140 --> 00:42:10,240
He opens the doors with all his might.

974
00:42:10,470 --> 00:42:13,480
Welcome back. You went? Amazing.

975
00:42:13,680 --> 00:42:15,040
I went.

976
00:42:15,650 --> 00:42:18,280
Thank you for doing your best.

977
00:42:18,280 --> 00:42:20,080
Chinatsu is delighted.

978
00:42:20,080 --> 00:42:22,850
He did his best for Chinatsu.

979
00:42:23,190 --> 00:42:24,750
Boiling the red tonguesole

980
00:42:24,750 --> 00:42:28,260
grilling the seabream in soy sauce and serving the squid raw.

981
00:42:28,390 --> 00:42:29,660
Let's eat.

982
00:42:28,390 --> 00:42:31,950
Father

983
00:42:29,660 --> 00:42:33,360
Of course the Shoudo island-born father loves his fish.

984
00:42:33,700 --> 00:42:37,270
His first meal was also a white-fleshed fish.

985
00:42:37,730 --> 00:42:42,540
This is also Chinatsu's first taste of white fish.

986
00:42:38,940 --> 00:42:41,170
How nice.

987
00:42:42,710 --> 00:42:45,110
Your brother bought these.

988
00:42:46,110 --> 00:42:48,140
Now able to go on errands

989
00:42:48,140 --> 00:42:51,080
who is the big brother in the giraffe class.

990
00:42:51,410 --> 00:42:53,850
Surely it's Rintarou.

991
00:42:53,850 --> 00:42:56,250
What a magnificent big brother.

992
00:42:57,720 --> 00:42:59,920
Nice errand.

993
00:43:10,700 --> 00:43:13,570
Nice errand.

994
00:43:14,170 --> 00:43:18,070
Adults speak within a in-the-know context

995
00:43:18,070 --> 00:43:21,010
but white-fleshed fish isn't conveyed well.

996
00:43:21,010 --> 00:43:23,180
He heard it as simply white fish.

997
00:43:23,180 --> 00:43:27,250
In general, with small children - like with kamaboko earlier -

998
00:43:27,250 --> 00:43:31,750
a lot of them think that kamabo swims in the ocean like that paste.

999
00:43:31,750 --> 00:43:36,760
So he will try to avert his eyes as the sea bream is being cut

1000
00:43:36,760 --> 00:43:41,860
and while feeling sorry for its pain he will still look on.

1001
00:43:41,860 --> 00:43:43,200
I think that's really nice.

1002
00:43:43,200 --> 00:43:46,370
I have a big brother so I've often noticed that

1003
00:43:46,370 --> 00:43:49,410
a younger sister usually only sees their strong side.

1004
00:43:49,410 --> 00:43:55,510
Even when he was on his way home his attitude changed positively.

1005
00:43:55,510 --> 00:43:57,750
So to see the troubles of an older brother

1006
00:43:57,750 --> 00:43:58,950
really made me emotional.

1007
00:43:58,950 --> 00:44:03,690
Speaking of brothers... Amami.

1008
00:44:01,020 --> 00:44:03,690
Yes, it's true that I have both a big and a little brother.

1009
00:44:03,690 --> 00:44:08,190
I really thought about how the brother did his best.

1010
00:44:08,190 --> 00:44:12,230
We often went to the ocean near Toyama during the summer.

1011
00:44:12,230 --> 00:44:16,900
One time it poured down. And I was so cold.

1012
00:44:16,900 --> 00:44:18,730
I was so scared that I started crying.

1013
00:44:18,730 --> 00:44:20,900
We were both huddled under a bath towel.

1014
00:44:20,900 --> 00:44:22,840
and said "you can have it".

1015
00:44:21,940 --> 00:44:24,120
How gentle.

1016
00:44:22,840 --> 00:44:25,910
My older brother was surely cold too

1017
00:44:25,910 --> 00:44:28,910
and this segment made me think of that.

1018
00:44:28,910 --> 00:44:31,250
You are crying?

1019
00:44:29,710 --> 00:44:31,250
I'm sorry.

1020
00:44:31,250 --> 00:44:34,680
I'm moved by your lovely story.

1021
00:44:34,680 --> 00:44:38,220
You are not crying during a segment but during our talks in between!?

1022
00:44:38,220 --> 00:44:39,790
They sound so gentle.

1023
00:44:39,790 --> 00:44:43,030
I'm sorry.

1024
00:44:40,460 --> 00:44:43,030
I can't believe that this happened during our talks.

1025
00:44:43,030 --> 00:44:44,590
And for our next errand.

1026
00:44:44,590 --> 00:44:49,900
A thrifty boy on an adventure to man up for his beloved father.

1027
00:44:50,630 --> 00:44:58,240
In Aizu, the town of Kitakata which is homophonic with Northway and is famous for their Kitakata ramen.

1028
00:44:58,240 --> 00:45:00,110
With its doughy and voluminous noodles.

1029
00:45:00,110 --> 00:45:04,450
With its thick noodles covered in broth. It's the best!

1030
00:45:04,810 --> 00:45:09,520
When speaking of Kitakata ramen, the soup can vary from seafood broth to animal broth.

1031
00:45:09,520 --> 00:45:11,590
From light flavor to strong flavor.

1032
00:45:11,590 --> 00:45:14,360
In this town with a population of just under 50,000.

1033
00:45:14,360 --> 00:45:16,990
There are over 100 joints.

1034
00:45:17,230 --> 00:45:23,700
And this joint that's been operational for 36 years is run by a father who wants to put their child to an errand.

1035
00:45:23,700 --> 00:45:27,540
Who from Sendai has taken over the joint just recently.

1036
00:45:28,270 --> 00:45:33,880
This fighter who is wearing the same clothes as the owner is the 3 years and 9 months old Ao.

1037
00:45:33,080 --> 00:45:35,080
3 years?

1038
00:45:33,880 --> 00:45:39,780
But at home where the owner is simply papa Ao is treated sweetly.

1039
00:45:40,820 --> 00:45:44,120
But her mother has raised his older siblings with tough love.

1040
00:45:44,120 --> 00:45:47,320
But even she has a sweet spot for Ao.

1041
00:45:47,620 --> 00:45:51,460
Since he's the youngest and just about cute

1042
00:45:51,460 --> 00:45:55,730
I can't help but treat him with cuteness.

1043
00:45:55,730 --> 00:46:02,040
He's always looking at his brothers and sisters and is perfectly capable.

1044
00:46:02,040 --> 00:46:06,140
He helps out with various things even cooking. However....

1045
00:46:07,980 --> 00:46:10,780
He's still drinking milk from a bottle?

1046
00:46:11,280 --> 00:46:13,780
He likes it too much to stop.

1047
00:46:14,950 --> 00:46:19,920
Ao has looked up to his father since he became a restaurant owner.

1048
00:46:19,920 --> 00:46:22,930
He wants to be cool like his father and work.

1049
00:46:23,730 --> 00:46:26,330
Their home is just behind the joint.

1050
00:46:27,530 --> 00:46:30,900
Ao, it's time for you to put on your work clothes.

1051
00:46:31,430 --> 00:46:34,770
Getting dressed for work.

1052
00:46:34,770 --> 00:46:37,240
Cool.

1053
00:46:37,810 --> 00:46:41,440
Look at the face. He's ready for work.

1054
00:46:42,280 --> 00:46:46,080
Remember when we talked about what type of ramen kids would like?

1055
00:46:46,080 --> 00:46:48,320
They discussed it yesterday with the owner

1056
00:46:48,320 --> 00:46:50,450
to change the children's ramen

1057
00:46:50,450 --> 00:46:52,620
They brainstormed on paper.

1058
00:46:52,620 --> 00:46:55,220
They would need some petit noodles.

1059
00:46:55,220 --> 00:47:00,000
Currently the freebie is some candy but what if they change it to toys?

1060
00:46:57,790 --> 00:47:00,000
- Kamen Rider toy
- Stickers

1061
00:47:00,200 --> 00:47:02,000
Would be lovely with toys.

1062
00:47:02,000 --> 00:47:03,870
They will adopt Ao's idea.

1063
00:47:03,870 --> 00:47:06,900
Papa said that it would be nice with a gachapon.

1064
00:47:03,870 --> 00:47:13,340
Gachapon: Capsule-toy from a vending machine.

1065
00:47:07,070 --> 00:47:10,040
He is usually told not to get gachapon by himself

1066
00:47:10,040 --> 00:47:13,340
but this time it will be his errand.

1067
00:47:13,340 --> 00:47:16,450
We want an Anpanman gachapon.

1068
00:47:16,450 --> 00:47:19,880
Eh? Not getting a Kamen Rider toy?

1069
00:47:19,880 --> 00:47:24,150
But only boys will be happy with a Kamen Rider toy, right?

1070
00:47:24,150 --> 00:47:26,820
I see, equal rights.

1071
00:47:26,820 --> 00:47:29,690
I'm asking you, okay?

1072
00:47:27,720 --> 00:47:29,690
A gachapon errand.

1073
00:47:30,030 --> 00:47:32,630
But you need them for your experiment.

1074
00:47:32,630 --> 00:47:36,070
First he will bring an apron to his father's work place.

1075
00:47:36,070 --> 00:47:38,000
Experiment for three.

1076
00:47:38,000 --> 00:47:40,770
The petit noodles is at the noodle maker.

1077
00:47:40,770 --> 00:47:46,140
He was asked to get gachapon from the supermarket and Anpanman kamaboko and milk.

1078
00:47:45,770 --> 00:47:48,110
He's only 3 years old.

1079
00:47:47,210 --> 00:47:50,810
Since they need 3 toys he can do it thrice today.

1080
00:47:52,210 --> 00:47:56,190
Remember to loudly proclaim
"Thank you for your hard work, owner".

1081
00:47:54,620 --> 00:47:56,190
Yep.

1082
00:47:56,190 --> 00:47:59,020
Because his father is the owner when he's working.

1083
00:47:59,020 --> 00:48:01,260
Off you go.

1084
00:48:00,020 --> 00:48:01,260
I got it.

1085
00:48:12,600 --> 00:48:16,210
